videos.description: Braxton Burmeister finds Cam McCormick for a 5-yard touchdown to put Oregon up 7-0 in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Ducks get on board after 11-play drive

videos.description: Utah's Leki Fotu recovers the ball after Braxton Burmeister and Royce Freeman mishandle the handoff.
videos.headline: Oregon fumbles exchange, Utah recovers

videos.description: Royce Freeman bursts for 34 yards to the Utah 9-yard line, which leads to a Oregon field goal.
videos.headline: Ducks get inside red zone with 34-yard run by Freeman

videos.description: Ugochukwu Amadi strips the ball loose and takes it 47 yards for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Ducks score on 47-yard fumble recovery

videos.description: Tyler Huntley escapes defenders and finds Darren Carrington II, who makes a 46-yard diving catch.
videos.headline: Carrington II makes diving catch

videos.description: Tyler Huntley breaks free for a 33-yard run to set up 1st-and-goal.
videos.headline: Huntley scampers to the red zone

videos.description: Utah elects to go for it on 4th-and-goal during the opening drive of the second half and offensive lineman Darrin Paulo catches a tipped pass while falling on his back.
videos.headline: Lineman makes sweet TD grab on his back

videos.description: Tony Brooks-James runs to the outside and evades tacklers  for 56  yards to Utah's 19-yard line.
videos.headline: Brooks-James hits the edge for 56-yard run

videos.description: Charles Nelson stumbles, but manages to stay on his feet to find Jacob Breeland in the end zone for a 22-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Nelson stumbles, makes TD

videos.description: Royce Freeman shows off his speed for a 38-yard run to set up another Oregon touchdown.
videos.headline: Freeman finds a hole for 38-yard run

videos.description: Tony Brooks-James escapes defenders for a 23-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Brooks-James makes defenders miss for TD

videos.description: Tyler Huntley throws a strike to Siaosi Wilson, who brings it in for a 29-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Wilson's TD catch closes the gap for Utah
